How to run::

Command 1>
	gcc main.cpp -lGL -lGLU -lglut
				OR
	g++ main.cpp -lGL -lGLU -lglut

Command 2>
	./a.out

Note:- Please right click your mouse, you will get 2 options
		1.> No shadow
		2.> Shadow

		If you click on "Shadow" then shadows of spheres will come.
		If you click on "No Shadow" then shadows of spheres will be removed.


		If you have issues regarding how to generate above 2 options, please contact me sunny170101068@iitg.ac.in